38 (a) As used in this Code section, the term 'health benefit plan' means any individual or
39 group plan, policy, or contract for healthcare services issued, delivered, issued for delivery,
40 or renewed in this state which provides major medical benefits by a healthcare corporation,
41 health maintenance organization, preferred provider organization, accident and sickness
